@abstract:
Declared intent and purpose for Linguist.
@end

## Purpose

Linguist — This library is used on GitHub.com to detect blob languages, ignore binary or vendored files, suppress generated files i

## Anti-Purpose

This project is NOT:
- A fork or wrapper around another tool
- A monorepo (unless explicitly structured as one)

## If In Doubt

If you are unsure whether a change is in scope, ask.
Sensitive areas: ABI definitions, license headers, CI workflows.
